These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, australian
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, lizard
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, february
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, indie
There 2 different types of food: grapes, potato
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, swisher
1. the australian is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the person eating potato is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality         | australian  | japanese       |
| Pet           | lizard   | rabbit    |
| Birthday   | february     | april   |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | classical     |
| Food         | potato | grapes      |
| Cigar     | swisher       | tiparillo           |

