.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, black
2 different games are played: snooker, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, april
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, turkish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, water-polo
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, woodworking
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who likes black##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | sprite         | cola       |
| Color          | light-blue        | black |
| Game           | backgammon | snooker    |
| Birthday   | april        | august  |
| Nationality   | turkish        | thai       |
| Sport           | water-polo            | climbing        |
| Hobby     | woodworking            | skydiving       |

