.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, brazilian
City: miami, london
House: palace, futuristic
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, lavender
2 different pets are kept: hamster, horse
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, blues
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes azure is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
5. the futuristic house is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Nationality      | brazilian       | canadian     |
| City         | london | miami    |
| House           | futuristic   | palace |
| Color   | azure     | lavender     |
| Pet           | hamster     | horse      |
| Music-Genre         | salsa     | blues     |
| Transport     | snowmobile  | car        |

