2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, vegafina
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, onion
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, soul
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, chinese
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, green
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, van
1. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
3. the italian is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
5. the person who likes green is the person eating cauliflower##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| City      | venice    | rome   |
| Cigar         | vegafina | alhambra |
| Food   | onion      | cauliflower     |
| Music-Genre   | soul        | r&b        |
| Nationality           | italian        | chinese |
| Color         | ivory    | green |
| Transport     | van         | boat       |

